{"id":605045,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/【墙的妙用】中国官媒如何扭曲日媒中国无现金/","date":"2019-01-31T08:25:41Z","modified":"2019-01-31T08:25:41Z","title":"【墙的妙用】中国官媒如何扭曲日媒“中国无现金社会”报道","content":"<p>2019年1月19日，央视国际新闻频道<a href=\"http://tv.cctv.com/2019/01/10/VIDECEeVnXwqNS585lHIjOWN190110.shtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">引用日本电视节目画面</a>，称日媒记者在中国体验无现金社会后被折服，外国游客纷纷直呼“中国人太厉害！来中国游玩，一台手机就可以走遍全国！”相关节目视频在近日<a href=\"http://n.miaopai.com/media/xOOjKaMlRabpl87Uabs0QDawmnH0pz8u\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">被新媒体转发</a>后引来网民热议。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_605050\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验央视版1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-605050\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验央视版1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验央视版1.jpg 1397w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验央视版1-300x265.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验央视版1-768x678.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验央视版1-1024x905.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">央视国际新闻画面截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_605051\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒震惊.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-605051\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒震惊.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒震惊.jpg 2370w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒震惊-300x103.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒震惊-768x262.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒震惊-1024x350.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">“日本记者被中国无现金社会惊呆”；微博话题页面截图</span></p></div>\n<p>然而很快有细心的网友指出，央视的版本只字不提日媒节目中<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JVuSW-ZnF_Q?t=190\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">对中国无现金社会造成的隐私问题的质疑</a>，将原本较为典型的平衡报道变成了“厉害国”版本。而网上热传的相关视频，则是直接剪掉了日媒节目中的质疑部分，</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_605048\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-605048\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验1.jpg 1439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验1-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">日本原版报道中提及了中国政府可以利用无现金交易产生的大数据，并对此可能造成的隐私问题提出质疑；视频截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_605049\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-605049\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验2.jpg 1439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验2-300x170.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验2-768x435.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日媒体验2-1024x580.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">日本原版报道中提及了中国政府可以利用无现金交易产生的大数据，并对此可能造成的隐私问题提出质疑；视频截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>附1：</strong><a href=\"https://youtu.be/JVuSW-ZnF_Q\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">日媒原版节目视频</a></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JVuSW-ZnF_Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>附2：日本在一年多前显然已经“震惊”过了一次</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_605057\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日本震惊.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-605057\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日本震惊.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"381\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日本震惊.jpg 1582w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日本震惊-300x228.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日本震惊-768x584.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/日本震惊-1024x779.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">网页截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[11813,33700,37181,34088,33265,34241,33613,33617,9149,33711,26070]}